#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage all your communication channels in one place with Odoo<strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Marketing Automation "
"</font></strong>,<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Email "
"Marketing</font></strong>,<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Social "
"Media Marketing </font></strong>, and <strong><font class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">SMS Marketing </font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Gestiona todos tus canales de comunicación en un solo lugar con las "
"aplicaciones <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Automatización de "
"marketing </font></strong>,<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Marketing "
"por correo</font></strong>,<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Redes "
"sociales </font></strong> y <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> "
"Marketing por SMS </font></strong> de Odoo."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Accounting "
"App</font></strong>)"
msgstr ""
"Gestiona tu contabilidad con mayor facilidad gracias a un entorno "
"completamente integrado. (<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"Contabilidad</font></strong>)"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your team's and integrate them in all processes by adding "
"the<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> Employees App</font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Gestiona a tu equipo e intégralo a todos los procesos desde <strong><font "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Empleados</font></strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Move or reschedule the appointment (the patient is notified automatically)"
msgstr ""
"Mueve o reprograma la cita (el paciente recibe una notificación automática)"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to manage your entire "
"business from your phone."
msgstr ""
"Odoo está completamente integrado en una aplicación. Descárgala y gestiona "
"todo tu negocio desde tu celular."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo te ofrece posibilidades infinitas, como:"

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"Este solo es un resumen de las funciones incluidas en este paquete. Agrega "
"nuevas aplicaciones, elimina o modifica los datos de demostración y prueba "
"todas las funciones."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once an appointment is booked, you can see it in the <strong>Calendar "
"App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Una vez que la cita quede agendada podrás verla en <strong>Calendario</"
"strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:mental_therapy.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organise your events and connect with your patients/clients easily with the "
"<strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Events App </font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"Organiza tus eventos y comunícate sin complicaciones con tus pacientes o "
"clientes con la aplicación <strong><font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Eventos</"
"font></strong>."

#. module: mental_therapy
